General.Name: E-Data Teknoloji Pazarlama AS
General.Description: E-Data Teknoloji Pazarlama Anonim Sirketi distributes technology products and solutions to institutions and organizations in Turkey. Its products and solutions include network and network security products, antivirus, APT protection, printers, datacenter solutions, disk backup, secure print solutions, KVKK/GDPR, penetration-vulnerability testing, certified data deletion, system tools-desktop solutions, server/storage, application security, patch management, and backup software, as well as data security, such as Apricorn, CoSoSys, and Data 443. The company was founded in 2008 and is based in Ankara, Turkey.
